name: PaizuriAllinOne (different angles and types)
description:
Would appreciate images, feeedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

The Model I used for the V2 images is here titled "bloodsplash's Mix" MightyCorneo (good model overall but, also good Vtuber Model) | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

If censorship bothers you. (V2 is Now Available) I will be making an uncensored version either as V1.5 or V2, but in the mean time just add censoring, censor, bar_censor, mosaic censor, and any other censorship tags to the negative prompt, and add uncensored early in your positive prompt, completely slipped my mind as censors dont bother me. A lot of the images were uncensored so it should work.

A multi view paizuri Lora. Corneo's pov paizuri Ti and Akto's clothed_paizuri pose Lora are great, but I wanted more variety as I am a near mastophilliac (meaning I LIKE breasts). So, I trained this Lora after repeated failures (this one is no exception) I got one that works pretty well.

Corneo's POV Paizuri Embedding | Stable Diffusion TextualInversion | Civitai

clothed_paizuri pose LoRA | Stable Diffusion LORA | Civitai

I haven't tested with the above models; they could help.

this Lora can do pov, side, above, front( similar to side), paizuri+fellatio, paizuri+irrumatio, double paizuri, autopaizuri, ,perpindicular paizuri (his one sometimes doesn't work), and can give some decent fellatio without paizuri.

I suggest picking one Tag and not mixing them, although you could get some nice results maybe, haven't tried it yet.

I also reccomend the disembodied penis lora for some of them.

Disembodied Penises | Stable Diffusion LORA | Civitai

recomended weights 0.6 - 1.0

Might need to put monochrome and/or greyscale in negative prompt

tags:

PAIZURI: OppaiZuri

POV: pov.

SIDE: from_side.

FRONT: from_front.

BELOW: from_below. (one of the rarer ones to get successful)

ABOVE: from_above,

PAIZUR+FELLATIO: OppaiZuri+fellatio (optional tongue, fellatio, oral).

PAIZURI+IRRUMATIO: OppaiZuri+irrumatio, (optional but recommended close-up, pov, pov_hands, head_grab, fellatio, oral, irrumatio, cum_in_mouth)

Edit about the Irrumatio and fellatio It seems just putting them and not the optional tags somtimes helps and sometimes doesn't, so experiment.

DOUBLE PAIZURI: double OppaiZuri, double_paizuri

AUTOPAIZURI: futanari giving herself a OppaiZuri, autopaizuri, (probably the hardest since it wasn't trained on it).

PERPENDICULAR PAIZRURI: perpendicular OppaiZuri, perpendicular_paizuri (from_side or pov might help with this one).

im very new to this, so if anyone could offer any advice on this would be nice.

The image can look better or worse if you add OppaiZuri before the tag you select, look at the final 2 images to see what i mean.

the width and height can vary but they will usually work with 512x512, 768x768, but most of them should work with any width or height, it seems more prompt and seed dependent.

modelVersions.description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

can do hentai besides paizuri, since some of the regularization images had other things in them.

I'll make sure V3 is only clear images of paizuri.

the "penis" tag is usually unnecessary since it was trained that all gens should have it. adding the tag might add multiple to the output. should be fully uncensored, but if for some odd reason a censor happens add it to negative. (seems I got one censor bar in around 100 gens, so just add uncensored to positive prompt and it should work), While training forgot to add Autopaizuri to training, so that is still hard to get. irrumatio is quite harder to get as well.

AbyssOrangeMix (any version) highly recommended .

768x640 and 640x768 seem to be the most consistent.

recommended tags: penis between breasts, penis in cleavage, boy in front of girl (helps a lot), close-up,zoom-in (both help a lot for fellatio/irrumatio)

0.8 - 1 weights (0.6 works, but in my testing I didn't like the results as much)

DPM++ samplers recommended.

DPM++a or DPM++2M are good for penises/crotches if the generation isn't making one, useful for paizuris that aren't POV or involve multiple people. DPM++SDE is great, but struggles at non POV sometimes.

I would suggest mixing the samplers up; also suggest messing with the CFG scale
